name: Target Time
description:
Get as many points as you can under the time limit as targets appear in random spots! Do your best to make and beat your high-scores!

Assets used:

Animals, sticks, and grass models - Simplistic Low Poly Nature (Acorn Bringer Assets)

Skybox/background, trees, fences, rocks, bushes - FREE Skybox Extended Shader (BOXPHOBIC)

Character model - Distant Lands Free Characters (Distant Lands)

Shooting/impact sounds - Free Sound Effects Pack (Olivier Girardot)

Jump and sprint animations - Basic Motions Pack (Kevin Iglesias)

Button clicking sounds - Minimal UI Sounds (cabled_mess)

Trees, bushes, grass, rocks - Low-Poly Simple Nature Pack (JustCreate)

Shooting and run animations - Warrior Pack Bundle 2 FREE (Explosive)
